::KitKat::

She jumped a little as this bot told her where she was going in her 
own ship.  She knew that either this bot had a spy device, or was 
told. And since he mentioned Destructor, that might be a good place 
to start.  She walked into the lab and looked at Destructor. "So, 
what is going on here?" She turned and saw DarkMouse trembling there, 
as she stood near Destructor.  She smiled and chuckled. "Hello 
DarkMouse.  It has been a long time since  I saw you last.  I thought 
you had been killed by Aracnia by now? Last I saw you, you went into 
the ship with Quickstrike to get inside Aracnia's base.  By what 
miracle of the matrix did you make it out alive?"

She looked at Destructor. She wanted to ask him why he had been 
spying on her or waht tretchery he was planning.  But then again, her 
instincts told her that Destructor was loyal and to trust him.  She 
looked from DarkMouse and back to Destructor. "What is it that 
requires my attention at this time?"
